 button.
 5.
  Users shall be able to manipulate the sounds by interacting with the control
 panel.
 6.
  Users shall be able to stop sounds by clicking the stop button.
 7.
  Users shall be able to modify the tempo by clicking on the up or down
 icons located next to the tempo display.
 8.
  Users shall be able to pan sounds.
 9.
  Users shall be able to expand the grid.
