\begin_layout Enumerate
The system shall animate activated cubes on the grid when they are triggered
 by the step sequencer.
 The system shall stop the audio clock, playback, and visuals when the user
 clicks on the stop button.
 The system shall start the audio clock, playback, and visuals when the
 user clicks on the play/pause button.
 The system shall pause the audio clock, playback, and visuals when the
 user clicks on the play/pause button.
 The system shall feature hints when a user mouses over a button, a description
 of that button’s functionality will be displayed in a small dialog box.
 The system shall provide users with a sawtooth waveform using Web Audio
 API.
 The system shall provide users with a sine waveform using Web Audio API.
 The system shall provide users with a triangle waveform using Web Audio
 API.
 The system shall provide users with a square waveform using Web Audio API.
 The system shall provide users with a white noise waveform, this waveform
 consists of a full spectrum of waveform frequencies.
 The system shall provide users with a pink noise waveform, this waveform
 is similar to white noise waveform, but lower frequencies are emphasized.
 The system shall manage an audio clock to precisely schedule audio and
 visual events.
 The system shall supply effects that can be used to distort the the user’s
 sounds when they are triggered.
 The system will provide a pythagorean tuning system, this will define all
 notes and intervals of a scale on a 3:2 ratio.
 The system will provide an equal temperament tuning system, in this tuning
 system all adjacent notes will have identical frequency ratios.
